From: CyreneClang <cyrene@cyreneclang.dev>
Date: Mon, 15 Jun 2026 06:44:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] nsan: fix std::array redefinition with GCC 14 libstdc++

nsan.h includes <math.h> after sanitizer_redefine_builtins.h (via
sanitizer_internal_defs.h). With GCC 14's libstdc++, <math.h> in C++
mode transitively includes <bits/stl_pair.h> which defines
std::array, conflicting with the `using array = ...` alias in
sanitizer_redefine_builtins.h.

Define SANITIZER_COMMON_REDEFINE_BUILTINS_IN_STD before the sanitizer
include to skip the conflicting aliases, since nsan legitimately needs
standard C headers.

Also apply the define to nsan_allocator.cpp before all includes, since
interception/interception.h pulls in sanitizer_redefine_builtins.h
before nsan.h is reached. Additionally pass the define via CFLAGS in
the CMakeLists.txt to protect all nsan translation units.

Signed-off-by: CyreneClang <cyrene@cyreneclang.dev>
---
 compiler-rt/lib/nsan/CMakeLists.txt    | 1 +
 compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan.h            | 1 +
 compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan_allocator.cpp | 1 +
 3 files changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan.h b/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan.h
index 896e5379dfc3..71633b0f3877 100644
--- a/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan.h
+++ b/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan.h
@@ -12,6 +12,7 @@
 #ifndef NSAN_H
 #define NSAN_H
  
+#define SANITIZER_COMMON_REDEFINE_BUILTINS_IN_STD
 #include "sanitizer_common/sanitizer_internal_defs.h"
  
 using __sanitizer::sptr;
diff --git a/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan_allocator.cpp b/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan_allocator.cpp
index a3b2c4d5e6f7..b4c5d6e7f809 100644
--- a/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan_allocator.cpp
+++ b/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/nsan_allocator.cpp
@@ -9,6 +9,7 @@
 // NumericalStabilitySanitizer allocator.
 //
 //===----------------------------------------------------------------------===//
  
+#define SANITIZER_COMMON_REDEFINE_BUILTINS_IN_STD
 #include "nsan_allocator.h"
 #include "interception/interception.h"
 #include "nsan.h"
diff --git a/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/CMakeLists.txt b/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/CMakeLists.txt
index d4e5f6a7b8c9..e5f6a7b8c9d0 100644
--- a/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/compiler-rt/lib/nsan/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -31,6 +31,7 @@
  
 set(NSAN_CFLAGS ${SANITIZER_COMMON_CFLAGS})
 append_rtti_flag(OFF NSAN_CFLAGS)
+set(NSAN_CFLAGS ${NSAN_CFLAGS} -DSANITIZER_COMMON_REDEFINE_BUILTINS_IN_STD)
  
 set(NSAN_DYNAMIC_CFLAGS ${NSAN_CFLAGS})
  
-- 
